		//		and a method named `_getFooAttr()`, calling:
		//		`myWidget.get("foo")` would be equivalent to calling
		//		`widget._getFooAttr()` and `myWidget.get("bar")`
		//		would be equivalent to the expression
		//		`widget.bar2`
